{"tid":2438800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟幫幫美國手足好冇","createTime":"2021-03-08T18:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T08:24:13.000Z","uid":282501,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d302f765fc2d46975e8bca27e4c06c4824a7c55a","tid":2438800,"uid":282501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T18:31:27.000Z","msg":"被迫前往美國真前線手足<br />\n唔想靠攤大手板<br />\n所以決定自力更生<br />\n試過做黑工<br />\n但係一星期可能只有一日<br />\n根本維持唔到生計<br />\n所以決定同其他美國手足<br />\n開始搞美國產品代購<br />\n而且佢地既代購計劃<br />\n仲會將三成收入回報番同路人<br />\n希望大家幫幫手Share同follow<br />\n幫下佢地🙇🏻🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/yellow_world.hk?igshid=sbhnff7trtwl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyellow_world.hk%3Figshid%3Dsbhnff7trtwl&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=265fedbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/yellow_world.hk?igshid=sbhnff7trtwl</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom tg 老豆搵仔<br />\n<br />\n而家得300幾個follower<br />\n就算唔買嘢都幫手share出去好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312b335aa061342934265c081b5a16a78a16355d","tid":2438800,"uid":282501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T18:31:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a60b1dc7596f82e2d5138d0a7de794dca388c76","tid":2438800,"uid":282501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T18:36:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463e7c776e2e790d57b1026c615083b40cb3adc1","tid":2438800,"uid":282501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T18:36:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f6ad830a713e833a323d33fc3daf2094250781","tid":2438800,"uid":282501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T18:36:43.000Z",